lemonfish
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A tradename for shark flesh used as food, esp. in fish and chips; =dog fish, shark (as fish for eating), =gummy shark, =school shark, =flake.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: fishmongers'
